full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/7/2023 BIRTH CERTIFICATE Cara Serial "G" No. 0658038 MAYOR'S OFFICE OF NAGAROTE CIVIL STATE REGISTRAR The undersigned registrar of the civil state of the persons of Nagarote, certifies: That on Page 9, Volume , of the book of Reinstatements which this office carried during the year 1979, there is an Act that literally says: Cert. No. 18 - MARIANO DE JESUS CALLO PADILLA.- In the city of Nagarote Department of Leon at three o'clock in the afternoon of the day of March of the year One Thousand Nine Hundred Seventy Nine. Before the undersigned Registrar of the Civil State and Secretary who authorizes personally appears. MARIANO DE JESUS GALLO PADILLA and presents to be recorded the sentence of reinstatement of Birth Act dictated by the District Civil Judge of Leon at 12:10 P.M. of the nineteenth day of March of the year One Thousand Nine Hundred Seventy Nine in which was ordered to reinstate the birth act of MARIANO DE JESUS GALLO PADILLA who was born in this city on the Seventeen day of April of the year One Thousand Nine Hundred Three, being son of Manuel Gallo and Raimunda Padilla. I, the Registrar, certify having in front of me the reinstatement sentence. It was read and found conform, approved and sign.- - JULIA ELENA H. DE CHAVARRIA.- MAGDA GLANCO DE SILVA.- IS CONFORM TO THE ORIGINAL. BY PETITION OF THE INTERESTED PARTY, WE EXPEDITE THE PRESENT, IN THE CITY OF NAGAROTE, ON THE TWELVE DAY OF MARCH OF THE YEAR ONE THOUSAND NINE HUNDRED NINETY TWO. MARIA LUISA FONSECA C. DENIS MORALES MORENO SECRETARY CIVIL STATE REGISTAR CIVIL STATE REGISTRY NAGAROTE, DEPT. OF LEON I, Manuel Castano, certify that I am competent in the Spanish language and that this translation is accurate.
